{"type": "article", "id": 9830, "title": "“Creative Toolkit” 行李箱耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001019z2DIC9Yo6TxJAjSK.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t耳机品牌 Master &amp; Dynamic 日前与行李箱品牌 Zero Halliburton 联合推出了一个名为 “Creative Toolkit” 的行李箱耳机系列。这个铝手提箱里面设置了一个 MH40 或 MH30 头戴式耳机，一个耳机支架，一个话筒线，一个帆布耳机包和一个皮制线缆盒。产品定价 750 美元，<a href=\"http://www.masterdynamic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001017HEGs0X6mUaKzJ1iN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001017Dz9jna80Hcgv62P7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001017GS73FEDenhHMQ4Jp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001018GxULrQWcYDeOJNFz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}